# ============================================================================
# Documentation (optional - uncomment if you don't want to commit docs)
# ============================================================================
# README_*.md
# *.md.bak

# ============================================================================
# Keep These Files (Whitelist)
# ============================================================================
# Force include important files even if they match patterns above
!requirements.txt
!*.spec
!README.md
!README_COMBINED.md
!.gitignore

# ============================================================================
# Notes
# ============================================================================
# This .gitignore is configured for the Aprovador Fromtis API project
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit:
# - mysql.json (contains database credentials)
# - *.log files (contain runtime logs)
# - *.pid files (contain process IDs)
# - dist/ binaries (large compiled files)
# - .venv/ (virtual environment)
#
# Always commit:
# - Source code (*.py files)
# - PyInstaller specs (*.spec files)
# - Shell scripts (*.sh files)
# - Documentation (*.md files)
# - requirements.txt
# ============================================================================

